##A "Gun" is hard to find, buy the amount of warm gun encountered a series of rising

Micro-signal. NBWEEKLY

Introduction of function, new media with temperature

Community Gate, Company Gate, supermarket gate... people have been used to the staff with the forehead temperature gun to take temperature this action. With the resumption of work in most parts of the country to promote the resumption of production, ewen gun this product has become a minority "hard currency" , a "gun" hard to find.

By Sheng Qianyu, editor | Roo

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
(Source: Wenhui. Com)

345 yuan, 425 yuan, 455 yuan, 500 yuan, 521 yuan... a small amount of warm guns, within a few days after the price changes, want to buy 200 amount of warm guns, help the villages and towns epidemic prevention of a Hubei Agricultural Enterprises Headache.

But the seller is also deeply frustrated, manufacturers limited production capacity, the market simply can not get goods, "their own shipping also need to pay" , if not for priority support Hubei, she would rather not take this business.

Buyer Helpless: Purchase 200 amount of warm gun

The occurrence of new crown pneumonia, so that the demand for masks, alcohol, disinfection water and other anti-epidemic materials, has suddenly become a scarce commodity. But now, with the resumption of work enterprises, production and life gradually restored, Ewen Gun has become the latest focus.

The thermometers used to measure the body temperature are either contact or non-contact. Contact thermometer is more accurate, but the measurement time is longer. The frontal thermometer is faster and safer for the public to detect the body temperature of people.

(source: Xinhuanet.com)

Now, at the gate of the community, the gate of the company, the gate of the supermarket... can be seen everywhere staff with the forehead temperature gun to measure the body temperature of passers-by, which makes the forehead temperature gun, which was originally a relatively small product, demand outstripped supply all at once. Many enterprises and units that urgently need to buy warm guns to prepare for the resumption of production can not be found in drugstores and online platforms, only through acquaintance introduction, purchase on behalf of human flesh and other means of "seeking goods. ".

On February 13, Xu Daoheng, general manager of Hubei Fengnian Agriculture Development Co. , Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as "Fengnian agriculture") , a local agricultural enterprise in Xihe town, Suizhou City, Hubei Province, was informed that there was a shortage of warm guns and materials in Xihe, so has asked about a lot of friends, want to buy for the town to donate 200 amount of warm guns.

In the Wechat Group of Suizhou entrepreneurs, Xu contacted a shenzhen-based company called "Shenzhen Zhulu Culture Tourism Co. , Ltd. " ("zhulu culture") through a middleman to help them order EWENGUN.

At this point, the Ewen Gun has been difficult to buy, can order goods is definitely a good news. Feng Nian's treasurer, Xu Lisha, later added Ms. Zeng, the head of deer chasing culture, who said she wanted to order 200 warm guns. Ms. Zeng replied: "245 yuan / piece, 200 pieces total 49,000 yuan, not including tax, not including postage. "

Xu Lisa told reporters that after the other side sent her product information map, she retrieved this "health health medical infrared thermometer" from Taobao and other platforms, and found that the same price more than 40-150 yuan, but in fact are not in stock. At this point, the amount of Wengun shortage, even if the price is slightly higher can be understood, Xu Lisha immediately through the bank transfer, 49,000 yuan to the deer culture.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
More than an hour later, Xu Lisha suddenly received a wechat message from the other side. Ms. Zeng apologized to Xu and told her that she was too busy calculating the wrong price. The ewen gun should be 345 yuan per gun. "I (purchase) order is 330 yuan. " Ms. Zeng proposed, Xu Lisa can make up the difference, or choose to refund processing.

See each other's attitude sincere, and the town for the needs of the hot gun is indeed urgent, and the general manager of the company after communication, 14 morning, Xu Lisa will 20,000 yuan difference to the account.

After the payment, Fengnian agriculture anxiously waited for the other company to arrange the shipment. For a few days between the 15th and the 18th, the harvest farmers pressed for information. On the morning of the 19th, the deer-chasing culture was told by the middleman "Fan Zong" to Feng Nian agricultural general manager Xu Daoheng that the ewen guns had been delivered and that "the workers got shunfeng points last night" . Xu Daoheng asked the specific delivery quantity, Fan said "to arrange 90(branch) . "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Xu Daoheng asked when the remaining 110 can arrange delivery, the other side said "expected to be delivered within 25 days. "

A few days may not be long enough for general supplies, but it means something different for the affected areas. The situation in Xihe, the largest town in Suizhou, is changing from day to day, with 56 village committees anxiously waiting for supplies. After the discussion of the harvest agriculture, it was decided that the time had gone on too long, and the remaining 110 had to find another way. And the middleman fan total also readily agreed to 110 amount of warm gun 37,950 yuan returned to the company.

On the same day, zhulu culture returned 51,750 yuan (150 units of warm gun money) to the account of Fengnian agriculture via fan. Financial Xu Lisa thought, must be the deer culture returned more money, so through the bank will be 13,800 yuan (40 amount of warm gun money) returned to the deer culture.

However, it wasn't until Ms. Zeng forwarded the invoice number and the contents of the shipment to Ms. Xu for inspection on the 20th that she realized that instead of 90 pieces of goods, they were given 50 pieces.

The price is changing from day to day

"I was really busy, looking for goods, so it was very messy. " Regarding the problem of telling the quantity of goods shipped not matching the actual quantity of goods shipped, Fengnian agriculture felt understanding, special times, we support each other, when busy errors are inevitable. But then something happened, and it just kept getting worse.

At noon on the 20th, Ms. Zeng told Xu Lisha on wechat that she had placed an order for the goods to be sent to the town of Xihe for 500 yuan each. "300 from you, 500 from me. "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
For the 13,800 yuan mistransferred from Fengnian agriculture, Fengnian agriculture hopes that the culture of chasing deer can issue another 40 warm guns to the town of Xihe to offset the mistransferred funds, or send 150 guns to the town of Xihe to make up the difference in prices.

In response to the price issue, at 6 pm on the 20th, Ms Zeng presented Xu with a large order of 10,000 units, totaling 4250000 RMB, and said, "Dear, tomorrow 10,000 units, the price is all 425. "

Considering the material is tight, even if 425 yuan per expenditure, it is good to be able to buy it. But at 7:30 pm, the amount of the difference sent by Zeng made Xu think, "how expensive" -- Foshan 62300 yuan. "It is equivalent to the first batch of 50 units charged at 500 yuan per unit, and the 150 units ordered at the back are charged at 455-460 yuan per unit. "

Xu Lisha thinks, 6 when it is 425 yuan per branch, a little more than an hour past, the price is expensive. Since then, she has asked several different channels, some quoted 390 yuan per branch, some quoted 440 yuan per branch, but in fact are not available.

At around 2:00 pm on the 21st, Xu asked Zeng to send her the account number, but at this time Xu learned that the price scheme had changed again -- 13,800 yuan which had been mistakenly transferred before -- and took out a part of it to offset the difference of the first batch of 50, leaving 5,000 yuan If the purchase is continued, the price will be 500 yuan / branch.

Xu Lisha calculates that that is equivalent to the first shipment of 50 unit price, from the beginning of 345 yuan to 521 yuan. If the plan continues to add, the unit price also from yesterday's 425 yuan per branch, 455 yuan per branch, to today's 500 yuan per branch.

With so many customers and so few merchants in stock, Fengnian feared that it would not be able to buy, and that the price would rise again. At that price, it made up the difference between the first shipment and bought 40 more.

Seller's response: In order to help epidemic areas, accept refund

The reporter contacted the head of the chase culture, Ms. Zeng. Ms. Zeng told reporters that she was really helpless to this, "from beginning to end with good intentions in doing this thing. "

Ms. Zeng introduced that oneself is not the amount of warm gun production enterprise. During the outbreak, Zhulu culture was originally to assist the government procurement, the government letter of entrustment, contract orders are legal and documented. On February 13, Ms. Zeng learned from a friend, Fan, that the town of xihe in Suizhou city was in short supply of warm guns and supplies. Fan, who is from Suizhou, asked her to help Suizhou buy some supplies. Considering the buyer is in Hubei Epidemic area, since she has access to the manufacturers, perhaps can help, decided to assist in the purchase of shipping.

But then a period of time proved that many amount of heat gun production enterprises limited capacity, infrared sensors and other production raw materials lack, even if the original order has been paid for, can not be shipped smoothly, manufacturers can only do refund processing.

"We can't get the goods [ on the market ] , and we can't get the orders from the manufacturers. " Because it's really not helpful, Ms. Zeng hopes to give the money back to the local buyers in Xihe, who will find another way. But for the buyers, or do you want Ms. Zeng to send supplies. Urged, forced, "finally we took a part of the high price from the hands of others, and then sent to the Xilihe" ; "not only do not earn the price difference, but their paste in a lot. "

And for the price of Ewen Gun, Ms. Zeng told reporters, "7 days ago may be more than 200, but now take this price to the pharmacy, anywhere, is impossible to buy. "

As for the price increase reflected by Xu Lisha, Ms. Zeng said that the price issue is that the two sides have agreed to settle the difference, and the subsequent agreement will be made up to her. "If there are still questions about the price, the product or the goods, you can apply for the goods to be returned for refund. "

Xu Lisha, Ms. Zeng are inevitably feel helpless in the heart, one side is holding the psychology of serving villages and towns to make donations, the other side is to help the epidemic areas to buy supplies, did not expect everyone to see prices climbing, are busy "full of sweat. ".

"Niche products" suddenly become "hard currency"

In fact, the EWENGUN has always been a stable and niche product. "Ewen Gun is actually a niche market, " He Quan, chairman of Tianbo Education, which has been in the market for five years, said in a recent media interview. "before this, the national demand was about 200,000 to 300,000 units a year. "

But the new crown pneumonia epidemic, so that the amount of warm gun this "niche product" suddenly into the "public view. As a result of non-contact, fast measurement, the forehead temperature gun has become the most popular in the epidemic thermometer. "demand has increased more than 10-fold, " he estimates

The "sudden heat" of the forehead temperature gun can also be seen in the index of the Internet users searching for the forehead temperature gun. Baidu index shows, after January 20, the amount of search of ewen gun rises quickly, search heat rises quickly.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
(Source: Baidu Index)

MANUFACTURER'S DILEMMA: Capacity Increase Meets Bottleneck

Demand is rising rapidly, but in terms of supply, the forehead temperature gun is different from epidemic prevention materials such as face masks and disinfection water. It takes hundreds of different components to produce a forehead temperature gun, even if the production capacity of the assembly line can be increased rapidly, but it will take longer to ramp up production of core component chips, which limits the ability to ramp up production quickly in the short term.

Ms. Zeng revealed to the reporter that at present, Guangdong's Ewen guns occupy a larger share of the domestic ewen guns market, with more enterprises in Shenzhen and Dongguan. Reporters to "Ewen Gun" as the key words in the eye of the sky for primary search, showed that there are 45 enterprises, of which Guangdong accounted for 31.

Ms. Zeng said that the Shenzhen Ewen gun manufacturers she contacted had experienced a shortage of core components, such as infrared sensors, and that capacity increases were limited.

In the medical equipment bar and other information platforms for retrieval, we can also see that recently a large number of forehead temperature gun accessories supply and production-related content. Many manufacturers reported the lack of production accessories, but some enterprises said there are parts of the accessories, but no production qualifications.

The sudden increase in demand, and limited supply, so that the domestic temperature gun market "in short supply" situation. Offline pharmacies, pharmacies can not buy, online access is also difficult to find. Feb. 24, the reporter in Taobao, Jd.com and other platforms for consultation, merchants also generally respond to shortages. Some merchants said they had been pre-sold until May, while a few others said they had some in stock, but the price of a package of two medical goggles, a box of gloves and a thermometer had reached 749 yuan.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Many buyers turn to other channels, through acquaintances, such as human flesh on behalf of the purchase of "goods. ". In addition, because the enterprise, the user forehead warm gun purchase demand is urgent, during the epidemic period and many by the network transfer, the physical distribution and so on way carries on the on-line transaction, encounters the swindler is also not in the minority.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
With the whole industry chain after the resumption of spare parts supply rebound and cost reduction, ewen gun market supply and prices or will gradually return to normal.
